{"TopicId":128043,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Update Suggestions","CreatedByName":"Gelix","CreatedById":154833,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T16:37:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Gelix","CreatedById":154833,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-17T16:37:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI decided to start a thread to suggest new update ideas! But I unknowingly talked about something that was against the rules! So here are my ideas on a thread that has nothing to do with when the next update comes out! Here they are:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E1. Base Parts\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E2. A system similar to KIS (Kerbal Inventory System) and KAS\u00A0(Kerbal Attachment\u00A0System)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transfo